flowchart TD
    A[Anki loads add-on] --> B[__init__.py registers hooks and menu action]
    B --> C[Browser opens]
    C --> D[register_browser_instance stores current browser]
    D --> E[User selects a note]
    E --> F[editor_will_load_note injects hide/reset JS]
    F --> G[editor_did_load_note runs apply_field_visibility]
    G --> H{Visibility enabled for note type?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Hide non-allowed fields]
    H -- No --> J[Show all fields]
    I --> K[User clicks toggle button]
    J --> K
    K --> L[toggle_field_visibility updates config state]
    L --> M{Disabled after click?}
    M -- Yes --> N[Reset visibility and show all fields]
    M -- No --> O[Apply hide JS again]
